						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Fragment of stone built into the wall of Mallayya temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>13th-14th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This damaged record in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">13th-14th Century A.D.,</hi> registers gifts of land, oil-mill, money, vegetables and corn for the benefit of a temple (name lost). Other details are also lost.</p>						

